"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://siteorigin.com/wpml-translation-editor-page-builder-compatibility/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://siteorigin.com/wpml-translation-editor-page-builder-compatibility/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 01 Dec 2021 13:27:02 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=342053\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:544:\"<p>We\'re excited to announce that Page Builder is now compatible with the WPML Advanced Translation Editor. Translate your SiteOrigin Page Builder and Widgets Bundle content quickly and easily using the Automatic Translation option or manually translating the available strings.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/wpml-translation-editor-page-builder-compatibility/\">WPML Translation Editor &#8211; Page Builder Compatibility</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5184:\"<p>We&#8217;re excited to announce that Page Builder is now compatible with the <a href=\"https://wpml.org/?aid=88702&amp;affiliate_key=V5z6Km6VwAK0\">WPML Advanced Translation Editor</a>. Translate your SiteOrigin Page Builder and Widgets Bundle content quickly and easily using the Automatic Translation option or manually translating the available strings.</p>\n<p><em>WPML&#8217;s Advanced Translation Editor allows you and your translators to work more quickly and easily while providing better translations. The editor comes with key features like machine translation, a glossary, translation memory, spell checker, HTML-less editing, and more.</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/translating-your-contents/advanced-translation-editor/?aid=88702&amp;affiliate_key=V5z6Km6VwAK0\">Find out more about the WPML Advanced Translation Editor</a>.</p>\n<h3>Translating SiteOrigin Page Builder Pages Using WPML&#8217;s Translation Editor</h3>\n<p>Navigate to the page or post you&#8217;d like to translate. Locate the <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Language</span></span> meta box in the right column. With the <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Use WPML&#8217;s Translation Editor</span></span> option enabled, click on the plus icon corresponding to the language you&#8217;d like to translate.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_341935\" style=\"width: 2570px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-341935\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-341935 size-full\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1366\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box.jpg 2560w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box-300x160.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box-699x373.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box-768x410.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box-1536x820.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box-2048x1093.jpg 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box-1050x560.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box-313x167.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-341935\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Click on the plus icon corresponding to the language you&#8217;d like to translate.</p></div>\n<p>Use the WPML Translation Editor to translate the page content, either automatically using the <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Translate automatically</span></span> button or manually. Click the <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Complete</span></span> button when you&#8217;re done.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_342233\" style=\"width: 2570px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-342233\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1253\" class=\"size-full wp-image-342233\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-300x147.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-699x342.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-768x376.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-1536x752.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-2048x1003.jpg 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-1050x514.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-313x153.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-342233\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">WPML Translation Editor interface.</p></div>\n<h3>Links</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/page-builder/compatible-translation-plugins/using-page-builder-wpml/\">SiteOrigin Documentation: Using Page Builder with WPML</a>.<br />\n<a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/using-wpml-siteorigin/?aid=88702&amp;affiliate_key=V5z6Km6VwAK0\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WPML Documentation: Using WPML with SiteOrigin Page Builder</a>.</p>\n<p>Thanks for reading. We hope you find the enhanced SiteOrigin &#8211; WPML integration useful. If you have any queries or comments, please, let us know below. If you&#8217;re a SiteOrigin Premium user, please, email <a href=\"mailto:support@siteorigin.com\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">support@siteorigin.com</a> as queries arise.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/wpml-translation-editor-page-builder-compatibility/\">WPML Translation Editor &#8211; Page Builder Compatibility</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://siteorigin.com/wpml-translation-editor-page-builder-compatibility/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/