\";s:516:\"<p>We\'re thrilled to announce the Link Overlay Addon recently introduced in SiteOrigin Premium version <code>1.27.0</code>. The Link Overlay Addon allows easy linking of any Page Builder row, cell, or widget.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/link-an-entire-page-builder-row-cell-or-widget-with-the-link-overlay-addon/\">Link an entire Page Builder row, cell, or widget with the Link Overlay Addon</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7560:\"<div id=\"pl-337527\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-337527-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-337527-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-337527-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p>We\'re thrilled to announce the Link Overlay Addon recently introduced in SiteOrigin Premium version <code>1.27.0</code>. The Link Overlay Addon allows easy linking of any Page Builder row, cell, or widget.</p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-337527-1\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-337527-1-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-337527-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h3>Usage Example - Linking a Page Builder Row</h3>\n<p>Edit the row you\'d like to link by clicking the wrench icon followed by <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Edit Row</span></span>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/edit-page-builder-row.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1876\" height=\"326\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-336422\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/edit-page-builder-row.png 1876w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/edit-page-builder-row-300x52.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/edit-page-builder-row-699x121.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/edit-page-builder-row-768x133.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/edit-page-builder-row-1536x267.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/edit-page-builder-row-1050x182.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/edit-page-builder-row-313x54.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1876px) 100vw, 1876px\" /></p>\n<p>Next, locate and open the <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Link Overlay</span></span> settings section.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/row-styles-link-overlay-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"580\" height=\"1046\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-336421\" style=\"max-width: 290px\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/row-styles-link-overlay-2.png 580w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/row-styles-link-overlay-2-166x300.png 166w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/row-styles-link-overlay-2-388x699.png 388w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/row-styles-link-overlay-2-313x564.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>URL</strong><br />\nEnter the URL you\'d like to link the row to. For example, to link the row to SiteOrigin.com, enter <code>https://siteorigin.com</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Open link in new window</strong><br />\nEnable to open the link in a new browser window.</p>\n<p>The process is very similar for linking a <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/link-overlay/#heading-linking-a-page-builder-cell\">cell</a> or <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/link-overlay/#heading-linking-a-page-builder-widget\">widget</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-337527-2\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-337527-2-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-337527-2-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child\" data-index=\"2\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h3>Addon Demo</h3>\n<p>A SiteOrigin Editor has been used to insert the text below. The entire widget is linked to the addon documentation page at <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/link-overlay/#heading-linking-a-page-builder-widget.\">https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/link-overlay/#heading-linking-a-page-builder-widget.</a></p>\n</div>\n</div><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/link-overlay/#heading-linking-a-page-builder-widget\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"so-premium-link-overlay\">&nbsp;</a></div><div id=\"panel-337527-2-0-1\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\" ><div class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-337527-2-0-1\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec fringilla maximus ipsum. In tincidunt auctor viverra. Nam posuere, enim quis tempus eleifend, urna mauris commodo neque, quis vehicul