media-addon/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:84:\"https://siteorigin.com/speed-up-your-workflow-with-the-multiple-media-addon/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 03 Nov 2021 19:23:13 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=337067\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:490:\"<p>We\'re excited to announce the SiteOrigin Premium Multiple Media Addon. Speed up your workflow by adding multiple frames at once to the following SiteOrigin widgets; Hero, Slider, Layout Slider, Image Grid, and Simple Masonry.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/speed-up-your-workflow-with-the-multiple-media-addon/\">Speed up Your Workflow With the Multiple Media Addon</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"enclosure\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"url\";s:73:\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hero-multiple-media.mp4\";s:6:\"length\";s:7:\"6580056\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"video/mp4\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6357:\"<p>We&#8217;re excited to announce the <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/?featured_addon=plugin/multiple-media\">SiteOrigin Premium Multiple Media Addon</a>. Speed up your workflow by adding multiple frames at once to the following SiteOrigin widgets:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Hero</li>\n<li>Slider</li>\n<li>Layout Slider</li>\n<li>Image Grid</li>\n<li>Simple Masonry</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Within each of the above widgets, you have the option to add frames individually. Once the Multiple Media Addon is activated, a new <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Add Media</span></span> button will be available that allows multiple frames to be inserted at once. Click the <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Add Media</span></span> button to select images in your Media Library. If you&#8217;re using a Mac, hold down the Command key while selecting images. If youre using Windows, hold down the Control key while selecting images. Click the <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Set Media</span></span> button in the bottom right of the modal window to complete the process.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_337138\" style=\"width: 2190px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-337138\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-add-media.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2180\" height=\"444\" class=\"size-full wp-image-337138\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-add-media.png 2180w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-add-media-300x61.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-add-media-699x142.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-add-media-768x156.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-add-media-1536x313.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-add-media-2048x417.png 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-add-media-1050x214.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-add-media-313x64.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2180px) 100vw, 2180px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-337138\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Click the Add Media button to add multiple frames at once.</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_337144\" style=\"width: 2570px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-337144\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/add-multiple-media-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1365\" class=\"size-full wp-image-337144\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/add-multiple-media-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/add-multiple-media-300x160.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/add-multiple-media-699x373.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/add-multiple-media-768x410.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/add-multiple-media-1536x819.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/add-multiple-media-2048x1092.jpg 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/add-multiple-media-1050x560.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/add-multiple-media-313x167.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-337144\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">If you&#8217;re using a Mac, hold down the Command key while selecting images. If you&#8217;re using Windows, hold down the Control key while selecting images. Click Set Media to complete the process.</p></div>\n<p>Once the <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Set Media</span></span> button has been clicked, a frame will be created per image selected. You can then edit and customize each frame as required.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_337142\" style=\"width: 2190px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-337142\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-frames.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2180\" height=\"754\" class=\"size-full wp-image-337142\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-frames.png 2180w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-frames-300x104.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-frames-699x242.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-frames-768x266.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-frames-1536x531.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-frames-2048x708.png 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-frames-1050x363.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/siteorigin-hero-frames-313x108.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2180px) 100vw, 2180px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-337142\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Once your images have been inserted you can edit each frame as required.</p></div>\n<div style=\"width: 944px;\" class=\"wp-video\"><!--[if lt IE 9]><script>document.createElement(\'video\');</script><![endif]-->\n<video class=\"wp-video-shortcode\" id=\"video-337067-1\" width=\"944\" height=\"531\" preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"video/mp4\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hero-multiple-media.mp4?_=1\" /><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hero-multiple-media.mp4\">https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hero-multiple-media.mp4</a></video></div>\n<p>Thanks for reading, we hope you find the Multiple Media Addon helpful. If you&#8217;d like to read the addon documentation, you can find it <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/multiple-media/\">here</a>. If you have any queries or requests, please, let us know below. SiteOrigin Premium users can email <a href=\"mailto:support@siteorigin.com\">support@siteorigin.com</a> for fast and effective support.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/speed-up-your-workflow-with-the-multiple-media-addon/\">Speed up Your Workflow With the Multiple Media Addon</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:81:\"https://siteorigin.com/speed-up-your-workflow-with-the-multiple-media-addon/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"Unmute Slider Self-Hosted Background Videos\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://siteorigin.com/unmute-slide-self-hosted-background-videos/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://siteorigin.com/unmute-slide-self-hosted-background-videos/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 21 Oct 2021 20:28:26 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=335181\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:504:\"<p>SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle version <code>1.25.0</code> introduces a new Unmute icon setting to all Slider Widgets. The new setting applies to self-hosted background videos. Allow your users to optionally unmute slider background videos by clicking on an icon.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/unmute-slide-self-hosted-background-videos/\">Unmute Slider Self-Hosted Background Videos</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2713:\"<p>SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle version <code>1.25.0</code> introduces a new <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Unmute icon</span></span> setting to all Slider Widgets. The new setting applies to self-hosted background videos. Allow your users to optionally unmute slider background videos by clicking on an icon.</p>\n<h3>Demo</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/slider-unmute-demo/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">View a demo</a> using the SiteOrigin Hero Widget.</p>\n<h3>Widgets</h3>\n<p>The following SiteOrigin widgets offer the new slide background video unmute setting:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Slider</li>\n<li>Layout Slider</li>\n<li>Hero</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Settings</h3>\n<p>To display an unmute button on your slide background videos, navigate to any of the above-mentioned widgets and open the <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Slider Controls</span></span> section. There you&#8217;ll find the following new settings:</p>\n<p><strong>Unmute icon</strong><br />\nSlide background videos are muted. Enable to display an unmute/mute icon. Only applies to self-hosted videos.</p>\n<p><strong>Unmute icon position</strong><br />\nDefaults to Top right. The following options are available, Top right, Bottom right, Bottom left, Top left.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_335185\" style=\"width: 1776px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-335185\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unmute-icon-setting.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1766\" height=\"267\" class=\"size-full wp-image-335185\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unmute-icon-setting.png 1766w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unmute-icon-setting-300x45.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unmute-icon-setting-699x106.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unmute-icon-setting-768x116.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unmute-icon-setting-1536x232.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unmute-icon-setting-1050x159.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unmute-icon-setting-313x47.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1766px) 100vw, 1766px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-335185\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Navigate to the Slider Controls section to find the Unmute icon setting.</p></div>\n<p>Thanks for reading. If you have any queries or comments, please, let us know below.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/unmute-slide-self-hosted-background-videos/\">Unmute Slider Self-Hosted Background Videos</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://siteorigin.com/unmute-slide-self-hosted-background-videos/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"Schedule Content Using the Toggle Visibility Addon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://siteorigin.com/schedule-content-using-the-toggle-visibility-addon/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"https://siteorigin.com/schedule-content-using-the-toggle-visibility-addon/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 18 Oct 2021 20:12:51 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=334650\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:537:\"<p>The SiteOrigin Premium Toggle Visibility Addon now includes the option to schedule your content. Show or hide Page Builder rows or widgets using a customizable date range. When editing a row or widget, you\'ll find a new Scheduling setting within the Toggle Visibility section.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/schedule-content-using-the-toggle-visibility-addon/\">Schedule Content Using the Toggle Visibility Addon</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2048:\"<p>The SiteOrigin Premium Toggle Visibility Addon now includes the option to schedule your content. Show or hide Page Builder rows or widgets using a customizable date range. When editing a row or widget, you&#8217;ll find a new Scheduling setting within the Toggle Visibility section.</p>\n<p><strong>Scheduling</strong><br />\nEnable to display the scheduling section. Show or hide the row or widget between a selected date range. Once enabled, the following settings will be available.</p>\n<p><strong>Display:</strong> Choose between Show or Hide.<br />\n<strong>Date From:</strong> Select the date to show or hide the row or widget from.<br />\n<strong>Date To:</strong> Select the date to show or hide your row or widget to.</p>\n<h3>Toggle Visibility Logged In/Logged Out Using Shortcodes</h3>\n<p>The Toggle Visibility Addon has been expanded further to include a logged-in status shortcode. Content can be displayed or hidden based on a user&#8217;s logged-in status.</p>\n<p><code>[toggle_visibility logged=\"in\"]Only logged-in users will see this.[/toggle_visibility]</code></p>\n<p><code>[toggle_visibility logged=\"out\"]Only logged-out users will see this.[/toggle_visibility]</code></p>\n<p>The Toggle Visibility logged shortcode can be used anywhere text is added in your page.</p>\n<h3>Links</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/\">SiteOrigin Premium plugin page</a>.<br />\n<a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/toggle-visibility/\">Toggle Visibility Addon documentation</a>.</p>\n<p>Thanks for reading. If you have any questions or comments, please, let us know. If you&#8217;re a SiteOrigin Premium user and have any queries or requests, please, email <a href=\"mailto:support@siteorigin.com\">support@siteorigin.com</a> for quick support.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/schedule-content-using-the-toggle-visibility-addon/\">Schedule Content Using the Toggle Visibility Addon</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://siteorigin.com/schedule-content-using-the-toggle-visibility-addon/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35:\"Ajax Saving Added to SiteOrigin CSS\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"https://siteorigin.com/ajax-saving-added-to-siteorigin-css/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://siteorigin.com/ajax-saving-added-to-siteorigin-css/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 12 Oct 2021 12:50:57 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=333637\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:373:\"<p>SiteOrigin CSS version <code>1.4.0</code> introduces Ajax saving. Save in the Expanded and Visual Editors without exiting to the Basic Editor.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/ajax-saving-added-to-siteorigin-css/\">Ajax Saving Added to SiteOrigin CSS</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3636:\"<p>SiteOrigin CSS version <code>1.4.0</code> introduces Ajax saving. Save in the Expanded and Visual Editors without exiting to the Basic Editor.</p>\n<p>The SiteOrigin CSS Expanded Mode workflow previously required the following steps:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Open the expanded view.</li>\n<li>Make changes.</li>\n<li>Close the expanded view.</li>\n<li>Save in the Basic Editor.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Similarly, the Visual Editor workflow previously required the following steps:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Open the Visual Editor.</li>\n<li>Make changes.</li>\n<li>Close the Visual Editor.</li>\n<li>Save in the Basic Editor.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Changes can now be saved in either the expanded or visual editor using the new save icon. <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/ajax-save-button.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-333653\" style=\"display:inline-block;max-width:30px;vertical-align:bottom\" /></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_333651\" style=\"width: 1686px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-333651\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/expanded-editor-ajax-save-button.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1676\" height=\"800\" class=\"size-full wp-image-333651\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/expanded-editor-ajax-save-button.jpg 1676w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/expanded-editor-ajax-save-button-300x143.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/expanded-editor-ajax-save-button-699x334.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/expanded-editor-ajax-save-button-768x367.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/expanded-editor-ajax-save-button-1536x733.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/expanded-editor-ajax-save-button-1050x501.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/expanded-editor-ajax-save-button-313x149.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1676px) 100vw, 1676px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-333651\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Expanded Editor Ajax Save Button.</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_333648\" style=\"width: 1686px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-333648\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-333648 size-full\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/visual-editor-ajax-save-button-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1676\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/visual-editor-ajax-save-button-1.jpg 1676w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/visual-editor-ajax-save-button-1-300x143.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/visual-editor-ajax-save-button-1-699x334.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/visual-editor-ajax-save-button-1-768x367.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/visual-editor-ajax-save-button-1-1536x733.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/visual-editor-ajax-save-button-1-1050x501.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/visual-editor-ajax-save-button-1-313x149.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1676px) 100vw, 1676px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-333648\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Visual Editor Ajax Save Button</p></div>\n<p>Thanks for reading. We hope you find the new Ajax save button useful. If you have any queries or requests, please, let us know in the comments below.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/ajax-saving-added-to-siteorigin-css/\">Ajax Saving Added to SiteOrigin CSS</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://siteorigin.com/ajax-saving-added-to-siteorigin-css/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\