 your site\'s design.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-anything-carousel/\">Announcing the Anything Carousel</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9542:\"<div id=\"pl-321887\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-321887-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-321887-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-321887-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p>We\'re delighted to announce that a new carousel widget is now available in the Widgets Bundle, the <strong>Anything Carousel</strong>! Display images, text, or any other content in a carousel. We\'ve released the Anything Carousel with a clean wire template and a wide array of settings that allow complete customization to suit your site\'s design.</p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-321887-1\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-321887-1-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-321887-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-anything-carousel panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-anything-carousel so-widget-sow-anything-carousel-base-d844a3c079e8-321887\"><div class=\"sow-carousel-title has-title\">\n	<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Anything Carousel Demo</h3></div>\n\n<div class=\"sow-carousel-container \">\n				<a href=\"#\" class=\"sow-carousel-previous\" title=\"Previous\" aria-label=\"Previous Posts\" role=\"button\"></a>\n				<div class=\"sow-carousel-wrapper\"\n	     data-dir=\"ltr\"\n	     data-widget=\"anything\" data-item_count=\"6\" data-loop=\"\" data-carousel_settings=\"{&quot;loop&quot;:true,&quot;dots&quot;:true,&quot;animation_speed&quot;:800,&quot;autoplay&quot;:false,&quot;pauseOnHover&quot;:false,&quot;autoplaySpeed&quot;:8000,&quot;item_overflow&quot;:false}\" data-responsive=\"{&quot;desktop_slides_to_scroll&quot;:3,&quot;tablet_landscape_breakpoint&quot;:1366,&quot;tablet_landscape_slides_to_scroll&quot;:3,&quot;tablet_portrait_breakpoint&quot;:1025,&quot;tablet_portrait_slides_to_scroll&quot;:2,&quot;mobile_breakpoint&quot;:480,&quot;mobile_slides_to_scroll&quot;:1,&quot;desktop_slides_to_show&quot;:3,&quot;tablet_landscape_slides_to_show&quot;:3,&quot;tablet_portrait_slides_to_show&quot;:2,&quot;mobile_slides_to_show&quot;:1}\" 	>\n		<div\n			class=\"sow-carousel-items\"\n					>\n				<div class=\"sow-carousel-item\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n		\n		<div class=\"sow-carousel-content\">\n			<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-321891\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/dave-herring-KMMR__2LEQY-unsplash-small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" /></p>\n<p>Yosemite National Park is in Californias Sierra Nevada mountains. Its famed for its giant, ancient sequoia trees, and for Tunnel View, the iconic vista of towering Bridalveil Fall, and the granite cliffs of El Capitan and Half Dome. In Yosemite Village are shops, restaurants, lodging, and the Yosemite Museum</p>\n<p><a style=\"color: #f14e4e;\" href=\"https://www.nps.gov/yose/index.htm\">Find out more</a>.</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n		<div class=\"sow-carousel-item\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n		\n		<div class=\"sow-carousel-content\">\n			<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-321902\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/owen-rupp-E0KNh67l5pE-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" /></p>\n<p>Joshua Tree National Park is a vast protected area in southern California. It\'s characterized by rugged rock formations and stark desert landscapes. Named for the regions twisted, bristled Joshua trees, the park straddles the cactus-dotted Colorado Desert and the Mojave Desert, which is higher and cooler.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color: #f14e4e;\" href=\"https://www.nps.gov/jotr/index.htm\">Find out more</a>.</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n		<div class=\"sow-carousel-item\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n		\n		<div class=\"sow-carousel-content\">\n			<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-321903\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/adam-skalecki-8i-LoPR-Jmc-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" /></p>\n<p>Canyonlands National Park in southeastern Utah is known for its dramatic desert landscape carved by the Colorado River. Island in the Sky is a huge, flat-topped mesa with panoramic overlooks. Other notable areas include the Needles, the Maze, and the Native American rock paintings in Horseshoe Canyon.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color: #f14e4e;\" href=\"https://www.nps.gov/thingstodo/cany-mesa-arch.htm\">Find out more</a>.</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n		<div class=\"sow-carousel-item\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n		\n		<div class=\"sow-carousel-content\">\n			<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-321905\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/christoph-von-gellhorn-kjA82leKmJc-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" /></p>\n<p>Saguaro National Park is in southern Arizona. Its 2 sections are on either side of the city of Tucson. The park is named for the large saguaro cactus, native to its desert environment. In the western Tucson Mountain District, Signal Hill Trail leads to petroglyphs of the ancient Hohokam people.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color: #f14e4e;\" href=\"https://www.nps.gov/sagu/index.htm\">Find out more</a>.</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n		<div class=\"sow-carousel-item\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n		\n		<div class=\"sow-carousel-content\">\n			<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-321915\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/intricate-explorer-2MIPToQmVY4-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" /></p>\n<p>Theodore Roosevelt National Park lies in western North Dakota, where the Great Plains meet the rugged Badlands. A habitat for bison, elk and prairie dogs, the sprawling park has 3 sections linked by the Little Missouri River. The park is known for the Painted Canyon and the Maltese Cross Cabin.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color: #f14e4e;\" href=\"https://www.nps.gov/thro/index.htm\">Find out more</a>.</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n		<div class=\"sow-carousel-item\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n		\n		<div class=\"sow-carousel-content\">\n			<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-321925\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/john-peters-cGu4uuIWzJQ-unsplash.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" /></p>\n<p>Mount Rainier, also known as Tahoma or Tacoma, is a large active stratovolcano in the Cascade Range of the Pacific Northwest, located in Mount Rainier National Park about 59 miles (95 km) south-southeast of Seattle. With a summit elevation of 14,411 ft, it is the highest mountain in Washington state.</p>\n<p><a style=\"color: #f14e4e;\" href=\"https://www.nps.gov/mora/index.htm\">Find out more</a>.</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n			</div>\n	</div>\n\n				<a href=\"#\" class=\"sow-carousel-next\" title=\"Next\" aria-label=\"Next Posts\" role=\"button\"></a>\n			</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-321887-2\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-321887-2-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-321887-2-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h3>SiteOrigin Premium Carousel Addon</h3>\n<p>SiteOrigin Premium now includes the <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/carousel/\">Carousel addon</a>. The Carousel addon provides a Layout Builder within each Anything Carousel item. The Layout Builder field is a mini-instance of Page Builder, allowing you to add rows, columns, and widgets.</p>\n<p>Shortly, the Carousel addon will be expanded to include additional settings, features, and templates for the Post and Anything Carousels.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_321984\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-321984\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-321984 size-large\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/anything-carousel-layout-builder-699x414.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"699\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/anything-carousel-layout-builder-699x414.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/anything-carousel-layout-builder-300x178.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/anything-carousel-layout-builder-768x455.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/anything-carousel-layout-builder-1050x622.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/anything-carousel-layout-builder-313x185.png 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/anything-carousel-layout-builder.png 1212w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-321984\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Choose between a Text field or a Layout Builder in each Anything Carousel item using the Carousel addon.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-321887-3\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-321887-3-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-321887-3-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h3>Documentation Links</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/anything-carousel-widget/\">Anything Carousel Widget documentation</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/carousel/\">SiteOrigin Premium Carousel Addon</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div></div><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-anything-carousel/\">Announcing the Anything Carousel</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-anything-carousel/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"Page Builder Accessibility Enhancements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://siteorigin.com/page-builder-accessibility-enhancements/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://siteorigin.com/page-builder-accessibility-enhancements/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sat, 12 Jun 2021 09:07:16 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=315393\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:550:\"<p>We\'re excited to announce Page Builder version <code>2.12.0</code> and Widgets Bundle version <code>1.18.0</code> introduced wide-ranging accessibility enhancements. Users can now tab through all Page Builder and Widgets Bundle views, form fields, and settings, making changes as required without using a mouse.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/page-builder-accessibility-enhancements/\">Page Builder Accessibility Enhancements</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1531:\"<p>We&#8217;re excited to announce Page Builder version <code>2.12.0</code> and Widgets Bundle version <code>1.18.0</code> introduced wide-ranging accessibility enhancements. Users can now tab through all Page Builder and Widgets Bundle views, form fields and settings, making changes as required without using a mouse. Keyboard navigation is now available in the following areas:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Page Builder rows, and columns.</li>\n<li>Page Builder Layouts view.</li>\n<li>Page Builder History view.</li>\n<li>Page Builder Live Editor.</li>\n<li>Page Builder row and widget form navigation.</li>\n<li>Widgets Bundle form field navigation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you&#8217;re a semi-technical user and would like to view the work involved in these enhancements, please, find the pull request links below:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Page Builder: <a href=\"https://github.com/siteorigin/siteorigin-panels/pull/772\">https://github.com/siteorigin/siteorigin-panels/pull/772</a></li>\n<li>Widgets Bundle: <a href=\"https://github.com/siteorigin/so-widgets-bundle/pull/1206\">https://github.com/siteorigin/so-widgets-bundle/pull/1206</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you or your organization make use of Page Builder or Widgets Bundle accessibility features and have any questions or requests, please, let us know. </p>\n<p>Thanks for reading.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/page-builder-accessibility-enhancements/\">Page Builder Accessibility Enhancements</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://siteorigin.com/page-builder-accessibility-enhancements/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"6\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}