(513, 274, 'panels_data', 'a:3:{s:7:\"widgets\";a:10:{i:0;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:706:\"<h4>KinetEco, Inc. Administrative Headquarters (AHQ)</h4>\n<p>AHQ is located in Downtown Los Angeles at 123 Sunshine Drive in the KinetEco Tower  recently renovated to harness sun and wind power. KinetEco Tower is a full-scale alternative energy model thats also an architectural work of art. The structure has won numerous environmental and architectural awards, including being recognized for Excellence in Environmental Aesthetics in 2010, by the California Downtown Districts Preservation Council. That distinction came with a grant of 2.8 million dollars to help convert other Los Angeles city buildings into renewable energy partners, joined together on a common solar and wind power grid.</p>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:7:\"tinymce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"59b3091ae6b2b\";s:19:\"_sow_form_timestamp\";s:13:\"1504906417875\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:6:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:0;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"3bea3463-c82b-4415-b206-2ba5fc5f192c\";s:5:\"style\";a:2:{s:27:\"background_image_attachment\";b:0;s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}i:1;a:14:{s:5:\"image\";i:254;s:14:\"image_fallback\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"size\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"align\";s:7:\"default\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"title_position\";s:6:\"hidden\";s:3:\"alt\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"bound\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"59b3091faf847\";s:19:\"_sow_form_timestamp\";s:13:\"1504906201717\";s:10:\"new_window\";b:0;s:10:\"full_width\";b:0;s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Image_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:4:\"cell\";i:1;s:2:\"id\";i:1;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"82bacb18-df64-44a4-9185-131ac433ec86\";s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}i:2;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:527:\"<h4><strong>KinetEco, Inc. Laboratories</strong>and<strong>Research Design Team (RDT)</strong></h4>\n<p>Our laboratories and RDT are headquartered in Barstow California, on 125-acres devoted entirely to wind and solar energy innovation and experimentation. The laboratory is the heart of our companys research efforts, and plays host to researchers from around the world  all with the common interest in designing and developing the most practical, efficient, and effective alternative energy systems and products.</p>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:7:\"tinymce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"59b30b6bd469d\";s:19:\"_sow_form_timestamp\";s:13:\"1504906129067\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:1;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:2;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"0d924440-3d9e-401d-94ce-1ad208101196\";s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}i:3;a:14:{s:5:\"image\";i:258;s:14:\"image_fallback\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"size\";s:4:\"full\";s:5:\"align\";s:7:\"default\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"title_position\";s:6:\"hidden\";s:3:\"alt\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"bound\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"59b30b422a696\";s:19:\"_sow_form_timestamp\";s:13:\"1504906066370\";s:10:\"new_window\";b:0;s:10:\"full_width\";b:0;s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Image_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:1;s:4:\"cell\";i:1;s:2:\"id\";i:3;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"cd210583-09ce-41c8-88b2-f8defa3df7ca\";s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}i:4;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:534:\"<h4>KinetEco, Inc. Manufacturing</h4>\n<p>Our Manufacturing plant is also in Barstow, on a neighboring 50-acre parcel, and is the central manufacturing facility for the company. The plant not only produces alternative energy products, but also uses alternative energy to run the equipment and processes needed to manufacture the products. In addition, t