(545, 314, 'panels_data', 'a:3:{s:7:\"widgets\";a:4:{i:0;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:823:\"<h1>Why KinetEco?</h1>\n<p>Our K-Eco Solar Panels are among the most advanced solar arrays in the industry. Combined with our K-Eco Solar Battery (chargers) and solar inverters, they form complete photovoltaic systems  that are ready to harness and store the suns energy.</p>\n<p>This table shows how our 200-Watt panels compare in laboratory tests against our competitors.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span>And our <b><i>Complete Solar Advantage </i></b>package warranties every panel and component in your system for 25 years, so youll always have peace of mind that youve invested in a reliable energy solution.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-293\" src=\"https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/solar-on-house_113875009-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" /></p>\n<h2></h2>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:7:\"tinymce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"59b30eaad5753\";s:19:\"_sow_form_timestamp\";s:13:\"1504907984085\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:0;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"6a98d1d5-49b5-4643-a3f2-a1eeb9c8ca18\";s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}i:1;a:14:{s:5:\"image\";i:121;s:14:\"image_fallback\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"size\";s:12:\"medium_large\";s:5:\"align\";s:7:\"default\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"title_position\";s:6:\"hidden\";s:3:\"alt\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"bound\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"59b3122446db8\";s:19:\"_sow_form_timestamp\";s:13:\"1504908008105\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:6:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Image_Widget\";s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:4:\"cell\";i:1;s:2:\"id\";i:1;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"17480a35-0092-4752-9c69-2fb6ef7ed676\";s:5:\"style\";a:2:{s:27:\"background_image_attachment\";b:0;s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"