(617, 385, 'panels_data', 'a:3:{s:7:\"widgets\";a:9:{i:0;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:706:\"<h4>KinetEco, Inc. Administrative Headquarters (AHQ)</h4>\n<p>AHQ is located in Downtown Los Angeles at 123 Sunshine Drive in the KinetEco Tower  recently renovated to harness sun and wind power. KinetEco Tower is a full-scale alternative energy model thats also an architectural work of art. The structure has won numerous environmental and architectural awards, including being recognized for Excellence in Environmental Aesthetics in 2010, by the California Downtown Districts Preservation Council. That distinction came with a grant of 2.8 million dollars to help convert other Los Angeles city buildings into renewable energy partners, joined together on a common solar and wind power grid.</p>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:7:\"tinymce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"59b3091ae6b2b\";s:19:\"_sow_form_timestamp\";s:13:\"1504906417875\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:0;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"3bea3463-c82b-4415-b206-2ba5fc5f192c\";s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}i:1;a:14:{s:5:\"image\";i:254;s:14:\"image_fallback\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"size\";s:4:\"full\";s:5:\"align\";s:7:\"default\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"title_position\";s:6:\"hidden\";s:3:\"alt\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"bound\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"59b3091faf847\";s:19:\"_sow_form_timestamp\";s:13:\"1504906751451\";s:10:\"new_window\";b:0;s:10:\"full_width\";b:0;s:11:\"panels_info\";a:7:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Image_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:4:\"cell\";i:1;s:2:\"id\";i:1;s:9:\"widget_id\";s:36:\"82bacb18-df64-44a4-9185-131ac433ec86\";s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}i:2;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:527:\"<h4><strong>KinetEco, Inc. Laboratories</strong