-Eco panel_97466479\" 		class=\"so-widget-image\"/>\n</div>\n\n</div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-92-1-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.80018645121193\" ><div id=\"panel-92-1-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h4><strong>K-Eco Solar Panel</strong></h4>\n<p>Available in 200, 250, and 300-watt models. Designed for use in a grid and/or battery backup system. Our solar panels are rated the highest in the industry for energy savings and economic value. Our panels, when combined with K-Eco inverters and batteries, power the most efficient photovoltaic systems for residential and business uses.</p></div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-92-2\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\" ><div id=\"pgc-92-2-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.19919204474829\" ><div id=\"panel-92-2-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-image so-widget-sow-image-default-813df796d9b1\">\n\n<div class=\"sow-image-container\">\n	<img src=\"https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/K-Eco-bulb_AS_90630559.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/K-Eco-bulb_AS_90630559.jpg 800w, https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/K-Eco-bulb_AS_90630559-150x150.jpg 150w, https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/K-Eco-bulb_AS_90630559-300x300.jpg 300w, https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/K-Eco-bulb_AS_90630559-768x768.jpg 768w, https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/K-Eco-bulb_AS_90630559-270x270.jpg 270w, https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/K-Eco-bulb_AS_90630559-230x230.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" title=\"Energy efficient bulb\" 		class=\"so-widget-image\"/>\n</div>\n\n</div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-92-2-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.80080795525171\" ><div id=\"panel-92-2-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"4\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h4><strong>K-Eco Energy Bulb</strong></h4>\n<p>Our CFL bulbs shine with a pure, white light and use 75% less energy than incandescent bulbs, while providing the same amount of light. Theyre available in a range of outputs from 9 to 70 watts.</p></div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-92-3\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\" ><div id=\"pgc-92-3-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.19919204474829\" ><div id=\"panel-92-3-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"5\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-image so-widget-sow-image-default-813df796d9b1\">\n\n<div class=\"sow-image-container\">\n	<img src=\"https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/product_K-Eco-solar-phone-charger_101200134.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/product_K-Eco-solar-phone-charger_101200134.jpg 600w, https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/product_K-Eco-solar-phone-charger_101200134-150x150.jpg 150w, https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/product_K-Eco-solar-phone-charger_101200134-300x300.jpg 300w, https://kineteco