(104, 1, '2017-01-12 01:36:04', '2017-01-12 01:36:04', '<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-105 size-large\" src=\"https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/home-with-solar-panels_173298905-1024x683.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" />Choosing to go solar is a big decision, and also a very personal one. Talk to anyone who\'s installed solar, and you\'llhear a variety of reasons for why they madethe choice. However, the top reasons for making the investment in a photovoltaic system are:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Protect the environment: Solar is a 100% clean energy source.</li>\r\n 	<li>Save money: Cut your electricity bill and take advantage of tax credits and rebates.</li>\r\n 	<li>Make money: Sell excess energy back to the utility company.</li>\r\n 	<li>Invest in your home: Solar begins paying itself back immediately and has a life expectancy of 25 years.</li>\r\n 	<li>Be a trend-setter: Renewable, clean energy is the future.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nWhatever your reason, solar is a solid investment that will reward you nicely for many years to come.', 'Five reasons to go solar', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'five-reasons-to-go-solar', '', '', '2017-01-28 02:11:35', '2017-01-28 02:11:35', '', 0, 'https://kinetecoinc.com/?p=104', 0, 'post', '', 0),
