(161, 1, '2017-08-11 23:31:11', '2017-08-11 23:31:11', '<h1>Make a difference every day!</h1>\n<img class=\"alignright wp-image-180\" src=\"https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/AdobeStock_60834105-300x200.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" />\n\nAre you passionate about science, the environment, and people? Do you believe that hard work can be fun and fulfilling? Are you interested in working with a team of like-minded individuals who are devoted to making the world a better place? Then a career at KinetEco, Inc. might be just what you\'re looking for. At KinetEco, Inc. we love what we do, and we\'re energized by our culture and mission. As one of the leading alternative energy companies on the planet, we\'re always looking for bright and talented people, who are high achievers in their fields, and have unique and varied backgrounds. Our benefits package is consistently rated one of the most generous in the industry and includes vacation time, sick leave, an employer-matching 401K plan, stock options, a wide selection of health, dental, and disability plans, wellness benefits, catered breakfast, lunch, and snacks, and much more.\n\nTake a look at our current job openings, to see if we\'re hiring in your area of expertise:\n\n<a href=\"#\">Customer Service Specialist</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://kinetecoinc.com/2017/06/15/are-you-an-experienced-developmental-editor/\">Developmental Editor</a>\n\n<a href=\"#\">Enterprise Sales Representative</a>\n\n<a href=\"#\">Environmental Scientist I</a>\n\n<a href=\"#\">Environmental Scientist II</a>\n\n<a href=\"#\">Human Resources Specialist</a>\n\n<a href=\"#\">Marketing Supervisor</a>\n\n<a href=\"#\">Mechanical Engineer, PhD</a>\n\n<a href=\"#\">Mechanical Engineer, Entry-Level</a>\n\n<a href=\"#\">Solar Energy Technician I</a>\n\n<a href=\"#\">Solar Energy Technician II</a>\n\n&nbsp;', 'Careers', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '142-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-08-11 23:31:11', '2017-08-11 23:31:11