(292, 1, '2017-09-08 21:39:45', '2017-09-08 21:39:45', '<div id=\"pl-146\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-146-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\" ><div id=\"pgc-146-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.81549471064095\" ><div id=\"panel-146-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h4>KinetEco, Inc. Administrative Headquarters (AHQ)</h4>\n<p>AHQ is located in Downtown Los Angeles at 123 Sunshine Drive in the KinetEco Tower  recently renovated to harness sun and wind power. KinetEco Tower is a full-scale alternative energy model thats also an architectural work of art. The structure has won numerous environmental and architectural awards, including being recognized for Excellence in Environmental Aesthetics in 2010, by the California Downtown Districts Preservation Council. That distinction came with a grant of 2.8 million dollars to help convert other Los Angeles city buildings into renewable energy partners, joined together on a common solar and wind power grid.</p></div>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-146-0-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.18450528935905\" ><div id=\"panel-146-0-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-image so-widget-sow-image-default-813df796d9b1\">\n\n<div class=\"sow-image-container\">\n	<img src=\"https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/KinetEco-HQ-building_LYNDA_15416.jpg\" width=\"533\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/KinetEco-HQ-building_LYNDA_15416.jpg 533w, https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/KinetEco-HQ-building_LYNDA_15416-200x300.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 533px) 100vw, 533px\" title=\"KinetEco HQ building_LYNDA_15416\" 		class=\"so-widget-image\"/>\n</div>\n\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-146-1\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\" ><div id=\"pgc-146-1-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.761356565028\" ><div id=\"panel-146-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h4><strong>KinetEco, Inc. Laboratories</strong>and<strong>Research Design Team (RDT)</strong></h4>\n<p>Our laboratories and RDT are headquartered in Barstow California, on 125-acres devoted entirely to wind and solar energy innovation and experimentation. The laboratory is the heart of our companys research efforts, and plays host to researchers from around the world  all with the common interest in designing and developing the most practical, efficient, and effective alternative energy systems and products.</p></div>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-146-1-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.238643434972\" ><div id=\"panel-146-1-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-image so-widget-sow-image-default-813df796d9b1\">\n\n<div class=\"sow-image-container\">\n	<img src=\"https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Kineteco-research-design-team_LYNDA_15367.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Kineteco-research-design-team_LYNDA_15367.jpg 800w, https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Kineteco-research-design-team_LYNDA_15367-300x200.jpg 300w, https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Kineteco-research-design-team_LYNDA_15367-768x512.jpg 768w, https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Kineteco-research-design-team_LYNDA_15367-272x182.jpg 272w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" title=\"Kineteco research design team_LYNDA_15367\" 		class=\"so-widget-image\"/>\n</div>\n\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-146-2\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\" ><div id=\"pgc-146-2-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-146-2-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"4\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h4>KinetEco, Inc. Manufacturing</h4>\n<p>Our Manufacturing plant is also in Barstow, on a neighboring 50-acre parcel, and is the central manufacturing facility for the company. The plant not only produces alternative energy products, but also uses alternative energy to run the equipment and processes needed to manufacture the products. In addition, the plant is heading toward becoming a Zero Waste Facility  reusing all plastics, metals, and chemicals required for the creation of KinetEco, Inc. alternative energy products.</p></div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-146-3\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\" ><div id=\"pgc-146-3-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-146-3-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"5\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h4>KinetEco, Inc. Distribution</h4>\n<p>Our Distribution center has units in all 50 states, and in 25 countries  and is a leading supplier of alternative energy products around the world.</p></div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-146-4\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\" ><div id=\"pgc-146-4-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.75948973242066\" ><div id=\"panel-146-4-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"6\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h4>KinetEco, Inc. Installation Support Team</h4>\n<p>Our professional installation technicians are stationed all around the world and are skilled in the operation and installation of all KinetEco, Inc. alternative energy products. From cabin, home, or small business systems, to massive alternative energy grid systems  our technicians are skilled in installation and troubleshooting, as well as performing regular maintenance.</p></div>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-146-4-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.24051026757934\" ><div id=\"panel-146-4-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-image panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"7\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-image so-widget-sow-image-default-813df796d9b1\">\n\n<div class=\"sow-image-container\">\n	<img src=\"https://kinetecoinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Kineteco-installation-support_AS_152394288.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://kin